AKA is brimming with pride after his mom, Lynn Forbes successfully reached the peak of Mount Kilimanjaro. Lynn who is fondly known as Glammy was part of the annual #Trek4Mandela team that made the climb up the mountain to raise funds for for sanitary pads for underprivileged girls. AKA shared a screenshot of a WhatsApp conversation he had with Lynn when she reached the top of Kilimanjaro. "Can’t believe you actually went ahead and did it!!! You’ve been speaking about it for years & years.  Super insanely proud and inspired," he said.